      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're an ai, i'm not asking for medical advice or anything. i just... i feel so useless. like i'm just taking up space and waiting for a pain that's never going to go away. it feels like there's no point in fighting it anymore, just fighting to stay alive when there's nothing left to live for. it's exhausting.",
